                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "En purs bébés que l’âpre vie\nDestine, – pour quel but sévère\nOu bienheureux ? – foule asservie"
